---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Access Control — OpenBiometrics" description="Secure physical spaces with face recognition. No badges, no PINs. Built for offices, gyms, events, and co-working spaces.">

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur-xl">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" class="h-8 w-8">
          <rect width="32" height="32" rx="8" fill="#6366f1"/>
          <circle cx="16" cy="13" r="5" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M8 26c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8s8 3.6 8 8" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">OpenBiometrics</span>
      </a>
      <div class="hidden items-center gap-8 md:flex">
        <a href="/#features" class="text-sm text-gray-400 transition hover:text-white">Features</a>
        <a href="/demos" class="text-sm text-gray-400 transition hover:text-white">Demos</a>
        <a href="/use-cases" class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Use Cases</a>
        <a href="/#pricing" class="text-sm text-gray-400 transition hover:text-white">Pricing</a>
        <a href="https://docs.openbiometrics.dev" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-gray-400 transition hover:text-white">Docs</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/drinkredwine/openbiometrics" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-gray-400 transition hover:text-white">GitHub</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="https://app.openbiometrics.dev" class="hidden rounded-lg border border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 transition hover:border-white/20 hover:text-white sm:block">Sign in</a>
        <a href="https://app.openbiometrics.dev" class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:bg-indigo-400">Get API Key</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 h-[600px] w-[900px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <a href="/use-cases" class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400 transition hover:text-white">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          All use cases
        </a>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Physical Access Control</h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Replace badges, key cards, and PINs with face recognition. Walk up, get recognized, walk through. Frictionless and secure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0d0d0d] py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">The Problem</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Badges get lost. PINs get shared. Keys get copied.</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Traditional access control systems are easy to circumvent and expensive to manage. Lost badges need replacement. Shared PINs create security holes. Visitor sign-in sheets are slow and unreliable. And you never really know who entered your building.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">The Solution</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Your face is your credential</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-400">OpenBiometrics turns any camera into an access control point. Enroll authorized people once, then recognize them in real-time as they approach. Sub-second identification with 99.86% accuracy. Works with existing door controllers via webhooks or direct GPIO integration.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">How it works</h3>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400">1</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Enroll</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Register authorized personnel by uploading a photo or capturing one on-site. The system creates a face embedding and stores it in a watchlist.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400">2</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Detect</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">A camera at the entrance captures faces in real-time. OpenBiometrics detects every face in the frame, even in challenging lighting conditions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400">3</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Identify</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Each detected face is compared against the watchlist using FAISS-powered vector search. Matches are returned in under 50ms, even with thousands of enrolled faces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400">4</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Grant Access</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">On a positive match, a webhook fires to your access control system to unlock the door. Full audit trail with timestamps, photos, and confidence scores.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries -->
  <section class="border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0d0d0d] py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Who uses this</h3>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#111111] p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold">Corporate Offices</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Secure lobbies and restricted floors with touchless entry for employees and pre-registered visitors.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#111111] p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold">Gyms and Fitness Clubs</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Members walk in without scanning cards. Reduce front-desk friction and prevent membership sharing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#111111] p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold">Events and Conferences</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Speed up check-in lines. Pre-register attendees and recognize them at the gate for a seamless experience.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#111111] p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold">Co-working Spaces</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Manage access across multiple locations. Grant or revoke access instantly through the dashboard.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Demo CTA -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Try the visitor management demo</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">See face-based check-in in action with our interactive demo.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="https://demo-visitors.openbiometrics.dev" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/25 transition hover:bg-emerald-400">
          Try Visitor Demo
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://app.openbiometrics.dev" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-gray-300 transition hover:border-white/20 hover:text-white">
          Get API Key
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div>
          <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" class="h-7 w-7">
              <rect width="32" height="32" rx="8" fill="#6366f1"/>
              <circle cx="16" cy="13" r="5" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M8 26c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8s8 3.6 8 8" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="font-semibold">OpenBiometrics</span>
          </a>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500">Open-source biometric platform for developers.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Product</h4>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <li><a href="/#features" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="/demos" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Demos</a></li>
            <li><a href="/use-cases" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Use Cases</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://app.openbiometrics.dev" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Dashboard</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Developers</h4>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <li><a href="https://github.com/drinkredwine/openbiometrics" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">GitHub</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://docs.openbiometrics.dev" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Documentation</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://api.openbiometrics.dev/docs" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">API Reference</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Company</h4>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <li><a href="mailto:hello@openbiometrics.dev" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="transition hover:text-gray-300">Terms of Service</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-600">
        &copy; 2026 OpenBiometrics. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>
